{"tid":2232993,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍得耐拖有咩時候你仲覺得對方好愛你","createTime":"2020-10-06T20:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T08:24:50.000Z","uid":357186,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ae4991a7c9fd54f0dcfe721bc900419ef235c734","tid":2232993,"uid":357186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T20:45:33.000Z","msg":"拍得耐左 對話好似變咗例行公事 見面黎黎去去都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實一直都有做好多嘢比小驚喜佢 但同時想佢擺我喺第一位 不過佢就無咩轉變 亦覺得我好專制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到依家關係好似去到樽頸位 我亦唔敢要求佢任何嘢 但同時覺得好耐無感受佢愛同緊張我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇返啲相 已經忍唔住流眼淚 再落去擔心行唔長 好唔捨得 但只有無力感<br />\n<br />\n不過我唔知係咪自己太多愁善感同要求高 想知你地拍得耐拖有咩時候你仲覺得對方係好愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849455413abf5917ba7146f8413f2acb98bf7982","tid":2232993,"uid":217683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T21:00:08.000Z","msg":"一齊咗幾耐"},{"pid":"516ee3ac607be4dd806b17910bde8c981eaf85b7","tid":2232993,"uid":234356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T21:02:03.000Z","msg":"有冇溝通過？"},{"pid":"df5481ccc9e0ef64839f2607ba41e9d9dc16aac9","tid":2232993,"uid":123456,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T21:02:51.000Z","msg":"佢唔愛你了<br />\n其實你都好清楚知道"},{"pid":"af8c7bc65f92df8d86a9bf99d9dfdd4b606f4756","tid":2232993,"uid":136936,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"ae4991a7c9fd54f0dcfe721bc900419ef235c734","tid":2232993,"uid":357186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T20:45:33.000Z","msg":"拍得耐左 對話好似變咗例行公事 見面黎黎去去都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實一直都有做好多嘢比小驚喜佢 但同時想佢擺我喺第一位 不過佢就無咩轉變 亦覺得我好專制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到依家關係好似去到樽頸位 我亦唔敢要求佢任何嘢 但同時覺得好耐無感受佢愛同緊張我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇返啲相 已經